snippet.title: Jody's Corner
snippet.description:
This channel IS NOT FOR CHILDREN! This channel focuses on everything POP-Culture! - Movie Reviews, Movie News, TV Reviews, Games, video Gaming, Music Discussions, Trailer Reactions and Live Streamed Discussions for adults
Website: www.jodyscorner.com
Podcast: Jody's corner Live! - Available on Spotify, Itunes and google Music!
Jody's Corner Live!: every Monday and Tuesday morning @10am-12pm pst!


I pride myself on transparency and raw "realness" with my audience. My subscribers are more than just subscribers. They are like my extended family! Jody's Corner is a valued opinion channel.


 People who view my channel will see nothing but 100% honesty! Im not here to be fake like a lot of others just to get fame and recognition, I am here because i am passionate about making videos to share with the world! come take the journey with me! I am still in my first year as of me writing this description (may 28th 2016), so come take the journey with me and lets get 100,000 subscribers together!
